@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Đặt vé 

autonumber
actor Staff as "Staff"
participant MainFrame
participant BookingPanel
participant SeatMapPanel
participant BookingController
participant ShowTimeService as "ShowTimeServiceImpl"
participant BookingService as "BookingServiceImpl"
participant Repo as "Repository Layer"
database DB as "Database"

== 1) Mở tab bán vé và tải lịch chiếu ==
Staff -> MainFrame: Mở tab Bán vé
MainFrame -> BookingPanel: Hiển thị BookingPanel
BookingPanel -> BookingController: getAllShowTimes()
BookingController -> ShowTimeService: getAllShowTimes()
ShowTimeService -> Repo: findAllShowTimes()
Repo -> DB: Query showtimes + movie + room
DB --> Repo: List<ShowTime>
Repo --> ShowTimeService: List<ShowTime>
ShowTimeService --> BookingController: List<ShowTime>
BookingController --> BookingPanel: Danh sách đã lọc theo POS window
BookingPanel -> BookingPanel: Render Date/Movie/Time matrix

== 2) Chọn suất chiếu và tải sơ đồ ghế ==
Staff -> BookingPanel: Chọn ngày/phim/suất
BookingPanel -> SeatMapPanel: loadShowTime(showTimeId)
SeatMapPanel -> BookingController: getSeatStatuses(showTimeId, userId)
BookingController -> BookingService: getSeatStatuses(...)
BookingService -> Repo: Cleanup pending QR quá hạn + lấy seat statuses
Repo -> DB: Query Seat + SeatLock + BookingSeat + pending QR
DB --> Repo: Seat status data
Repo --> BookingService: List<SeatStatusDto>
BookingService --> BookingController: seat statuses
BookingController --> SeatMapPanel: seat statuses
SeatMapPanel --> BookingPanel: callback onSelectionChanged()

== 3) Chọn/Hủy chọn ghế ==
Staff -> SeatMapPanel: Click ghế
alt Ghế AVAILABLE
  SeatMapPanel -> BookingController: lockSeat(showTimeId, seatId, userId)
  BookingController -> BookingService: lockSeat(...)
  BookingService -> Repo: validate showtime + check booked + check active lock + save SeatLock
  Repo -> DB: SELECT/INSERT SeatLock
  DB --> Repo: success/fail
  BookingService --> BookingController: done/exception
  SeatMapPanel -> BookingController: getSeatStatuses(...) để refresh
else Ghế SELECTED (ghế của mình)
  SeatMapPanel -> BookingController: unlockSeat(showTimeId, seatId, userId)
  BookingController -> BookingService: unlockSeat(...)
  BookingService -> Repo: delete lock nếu đúng owner
  Repo -> DB: DELETE SeatLock
  DB --> Repo: done
else Ghế PROCESSING
  SeatMapPanel --> BookingPanel: onProcessingSeatClicked(seatStatus)
  BookingPanel -> MainFrame: switchToCheckout() (mở lại pending QR nếu cùng owner)
else Ghế LOCKED/BOOKED
  SeatMapPanel -> Staff: Thông báo ghế không khả dụng
end

== 4) Hủy toàn bộ ghế đang giữ ==
Staff -> SeatMapPanel: Bấm "Hủy tất cả"
SeatMapPanel -> BookingController: unlockAllSeats(showTimeId, userId)
BookingController -> BookingService: unlockAllSeatsForUser(...)
BookingService -> Repo: deleteUserLocksForShowTime(...)
Repo -> DB: DELETE SeatLock by user/showtime
DB --> Repo: done

== 5) Sang bước thanh toán ==
Staff -> BookingPanel: Bấm "Thanh toán"
alt Không có vé và cũng không có F&B
  BookingPanel --> Staff: Cảnh báo phải chọn vé hoặc F&B
else Có ít nhất 1 mục (vé hoặc F&B)
  BookingPanel -> MainFrame: onProceedToCheckout.run()
  MainFrame -> MainFrame: switchToCheckout()
end

@enduml
